data.title: Tron Sales, Inc.
data.meta_description: At Tech-Tron Sales, we strive to be the most professional and responsive sales/customer service organization.
data.text:
At Tech-Tron Sales, we strive to be the most professional and responsive sales/customer service organization. We will add value to the end-user/manufacturer sales chain.

Our intellectual property is our relationship with our customers, our knowledge of their programs, and our understanding of their direction. We will be responsive and attentive to our customers/Distributor Partners and the principals we represent.
